{"tid":793456,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐宋詞] 一人多句寫得好靚嘅詞","createTime":"2018-08-25T12:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T04:30:08.000Z","uid":71004,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"4c00330e4f834e085d265f0eaba37d5a378dc6d0","tid":793456,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"風乍起，吹皺一池春水<br />\n<br />\n小樓吹徹玉蕭寒<br />\n<br />\n昨晚西風凋碧樹"},{"pid":"d731b4dd479eb531f628f74f7b485b54df2b88cc","tid":793456,"uid":134883,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"東風夜放花千樹"},{"pid":"7e751b4f407d5a1832546aeeb3172d074ca5778a","tid":793456,"uid":125869,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"今宵酒醒何處？楊柳岸，曉風殘月<br />\n<br />\n無可奈何花落去，似曾相識燕歸來<br />\n<br />\n當時明月在，曾照彩雲歸<br />\n<br />\n門掩黃昏，無計留春住"},{"pid":"4aec424d7c080a7588ff995713cd827313d03e8f","tid":793456,"uid":38684,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"東風夜放花千樹<br />\n更吹落，星如雨"},{"pid":"a03ac3d9fa1fca0c722864e7d7eff88e747a72cd","tid":793456,"uid":187076,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"尋尋覓覓，冷冷清清，淒悽慘慘戚戚"},{"pid":"1ca1f6ccb7f16ad9c56ce34f977d38b08d61bbad","tid":793456,"uid":171849,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"獨自莫憑欄，無限江山，別時容易見時難。<br />\n<br />\n問君能有幾多愁，恰似一江春水向東流。<br />\n<br />\n李煜既詞未必係寫得最好個個，但一定係最打動我個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90893c064eab61bc5d8034cb8329f82b277d9ec7","tid":793456,"uid":68457,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"王禹偁<br />\n雨恨雲愁，江南依舊稱佳麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柳永<br />\n衣帶漸寬終不悔，為依消得人憔悴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然有啲為賦新詞強說愁feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n李清照<br />\n東籬把酒黃昏後，有暗香盈袖。莫道不銷魂，簾捲西風，人比黃花瘦<br />\n<br />\n仲有好出名嘅但願人長久，千里共嬋娟"},{"pid":"c1baad897c2852fd644dbe2f2431bd5c59ee5f3e","tid":793456,"uid":165028,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"以前舊登有唔少巴打文學造詣好高, 又作曲又填詞咁<br />\n而家child登叫人quote幾句野都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267dffd44c76717fda083c2b7d3f0884e15e7e02","tid":793456,"uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"曾宴桃源深洞，一曲舞鸞歌鳳。<br />\n長記別伊時，和淚出門相送。<br />\n如夢，如夢，殘月落花煙重。"},{"pid":"c6c702217cda5bb06280136f0cd166c228f93d2c","tid":793456,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"267dffd44c76717fda083c2b7d3f0884e15e7e02","tid":793456,"uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"曾宴桃源深洞，一曲舞鸞歌鳳。<br />\n長記別伊時，和淚出門相送。<br />\n如夢，如夢，殘月落花煙重。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"可以介紹埋詞人名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c3e333417e8452f6da63080271ac2d4ff23cfd","tid":793456,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"張繼《楓橋夜泊》<br />\n<br />\n月落烏啼霜滿天，江楓漁火對愁眠。<br />\n姑蘇城外寒山寺，夜半鐘聲到客船。"},{"pid":"f4c5a6427e7c6e4e1c2482d32d7c181c4f6992b4","tid":793456,"uid":165809,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"淚眼問花花不語，亂紅飛過鞦韆去"},{"pid":"3bebde4c0eb3a48cc05cf8a535f5b2ad8b620937","tid":793456,"uid":123825,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"龜頭剝落生苺苔<br />\n<br />\n隔江遊𣈱後庭花<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c45e13ecd9ea67a775b71143b5b4a4a18fce24","tid":793456,"uid":179844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0763fbaf0a3b43ef923ae051d2a229258342791b","tid":793456,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:06:37.000Z","msg":"柳永<br />\n<br />\n佇倚危樓風細細，望極春愁，黯黯生天際。草色煙光殘照里，無言誰會憑闌意。<br />\n<br />\n擬把疏狂圖一醉，對酒當歌，強樂還無味。衣帶漸寬終不悔，為伊消得人憔悴。"},{"pid":"d678a663134a5288b58bac67ef9122bb43401675","tid":793456,"uid":4231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"月上柳梢頭 人約黃昏後"},{"pid":"299e82c42ee2b3e5495723462001326052dea982","tid":793456,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"長記曾攜手樹 千樹壓 西湖寒碧<br />\n<br />\n我是人間惆悵客 知君何事淚縱橫 斷腸聲裡憶平生"},{"pid":"9e4461ad3b9f6fffc0b904242d147cd67a4fadfa","tid":793456,"uid":38298,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T19:35:48.000Z","msg":"眾裡尋他千百度 驀然回首 <br />\n那人卻在 燈火闌珊處"},{"pid":"5b887831fa728598c53556a20035871fd7438b9d","tid":793456,"uid":199875,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"生當作人杰，死亦為鬼雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b226be9705e36d8c9df5c1e1a0d5ad3f1bd4ce2","tid":793456,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T19:53:09.000Z","msg":"個人認為蘇軾基本最屈"},{"pid":"03533c81980312fa0c0d32af59227480a595ebba","tid":793456,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5b