3b24d","tid":793456,"uid":32753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:00:10.000Z","msg":"好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:03:52.000Z","msg":"巴打未轉ac wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:04:40.000Z","msg":"我細佬佢未食藥，唔好怪佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:11:03.000Z","msg":"自己好自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8182f06afa7be81dc938afc42cebc6b5bc73f5","tid":793456,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:13:23.000Z","msg":"獨釣寒江雪"},{"pid":"d84827a24530d0bff46b1c64d131e41d058e183e","tid":793456,"uid":23115,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:21:31.000Z","msg":"歐陽修<br />\n<br />\n庭院深深深幾許，楊柳堆煙，簾幕無重數。<br />\n<br />\n月上柳梢頭，人約黃昏後。<br />\n<br />\n李清照<br />\n<br />\n花自飄零水自流，一種相思，兩處閒愁。<br />\n<br />\n晏殊<br />\n<br />\n天涯地角有窮時，只有相思無盡處。"},{"pid":"5741656aafe1ab869069c15965e59134cd9a6f34","tid":793456,"uid":26878,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1baad897c2852fd644dbe2f2431bd5c59ee5f3e","tid":793456,"uid":165028,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"以前舊登有唔少巴打文學造詣好高, 又作曲又填詞咁<br />\n而家child登叫人quote幾句野都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:24:39.000Z","msg":"又見到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享下陸游同佢老婆嘅一對詞 個人幾鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詞牌:《釵頭鳳》<br />\n<br />\n紅酥手，黃藤酒，滿城春色宮牆柳。<br />\n東風惡，歡情薄。一懷愁緒，幾年離索。<br />\n錯！錯！錯！<br />\n<br />\n春如舊，人空瘦，淚痕紅浥鮫綃透。<br />\n桃花落，閑池閣。山盟雖在，錦書難託。<br />\n莫！莫！莫！ <br />\n<br />\n佢老婆睇完之後回佢：<br />\n<br />\n世情惡，人情薄，雨送黃昏花易落。<br />\n曉風乾，淚痕殘。欲箋心事，獨倚斜欄。<br />\n難！難！難！ <br />\n<br />\n人成個，今非昨，病魂常似秋千索。<br />\n角聲寒，夜闌珊。怕人詢問，咽淚裝歡。<br />\n瞞！瞞！瞞！<br />\n<br />\n兩個被逼分開但又突然撞返 好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f759e6400a6cc09e07e8ee6321f2e8b8346e176","tid":793456,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d731b4dd479eb531f628f74f7b485b54df2b88cc","tid":793456,"uid":134883,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"東風夜放花千樹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:29:04.000Z","msg":"一見標題就諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374f27db9c53ba28f00b650e663c5beb0dd2da9d","tid":793456,"uid":77164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T20:44:18.000Z","msg":"蘇軾 江城子<br />\n明月夜，短松岡。"},{"pid":"9f7b75aa85c514324a40148d997cac00e322dd7c","tid":793456,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:05:01.000Z","msg":"東南形勝，三吳都會，錢塘自古繁華，煙柳畫橋，風簾翠幕，參差十萬人家。<br />\n雲樹繞堤沙，怒濤卷霜雪，天塹無涯。市列珠璣，戶盈羅綺，競豪奢。<br />\n<br />\n重湖疊巘清嘉。有三秋桂子，十里荷花。羌管弄晴，菱歌泛夜，嬉嬉釣叟蓮娃。<br />\n千騎擁高牙。乘醉聽簫鼓，吟賞煙霞。異日圖將好景，歸去鳳池誇。"},{"pid":"109fdb37615471753237c5c6c1426ac958f371ff","tid":793456,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b226be9705e36d8c9df5c1e1a0d5ad3f1bd4ce2","tid":793456,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T19:53:09.000Z","msg":"個人認為蘇軾基本最屈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T00:11:59.000Z","msg":"有人話佢d詞不協音韻"},{"pid":"5ec3ae4bee23201895c4be9956a87fefda94bb51","tid":793456,"uid":166885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c702217cda5bb06280136f0cd166c228f93d2c","tid":793456,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"267dffd44c76717fda083c2b7d3f0884e15e7e02","tid":793456,"uid":161781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:17:31.000Z","msg":"曾宴桃源深洞，一曲舞鸞歌鳳。<br />\n長記別伊時，和淚出門相送。<br />\n如夢，如夢，殘月落花煙重。"},"citedBy":1,"re