<br />\n啲方言應該就會同廣東話有越大嘅差異<br />\n咁呢啲方言係有機會係保存咗一啲古音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然佢哋都會受到以前越族人同其他族嘅口音嘅影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該都唔會係以前嘅唐宋古音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人推測，有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872bb66f4c178012ddf60639702ba128e7aa56ff","tid":793456,"uid":31501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T23:50:43.000Z","msg":"破陣子<br />\n<br />\n四十年來家國，三千里地山河。鳳閣龍樓連霄漢，玉樹瓊枝作煙蘿。幾曾識干戈？<br />\n一旦歸為臣虜，沈腰潘鬢銷磨。最是倉皇辭廟日，教坊猶奏別離歌。垂淚對宮娥。<br />\n<br />\n睇到都覺李後主有幾哀傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n虞美人<br />\n<br />\n春花秋月何時了，往事知多少。小樓昨夜又東風，故國不堪回首月明中。<br />\n<br />\n雕欄玉砌應猶在，只是朱顏改。問君能有幾多愁，恰似一江春水向東流。"},{"pid":"ec2c8c97960fad1f24146f4dc7a9d2d21856834d","tid":793456,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T23:56:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b841d15a471bbfd26124274e9901a65f9aa881fe","tid":793456,"uid":200686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T00:04:37.000Z","msg":"大江東去"},{"pid":"b28a7895c437c67eb4980d05c6dc4e7a273b3b84","tid":793456,"uid":110892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"人生自是有情痴 此恨不關風與月<br />\n<br />\n春蠶到死絲方盡 蠟炬成灰淚始乾"},{"pid":"c0e482276717cb46d71479afd0668508a5953d7a","tid":793456,"uid":199776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:43:26.000Z","msg":"衰蘭送客咸陽道，天若有情天亦老。"},{"pid":"08072d63fd494f9f33ae5c24a9d2f0c15d5de05b","tid":793456,"uid":177475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"玉人何處教吹簫 <br />\n富士香檳吃不消"},{"pid":"acca79cfa7063eaa669b5b806c3093aa1316c974","tid":793456,"uid":9717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"忽見寒梅樹，開花漢水濱。 不知春色早，疑是弄珠人。"},{"pid":"fb2ee